SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[NameProduct], [a].[DescriptionProduct], [a].[Price], [a].[CreationDate], [a].[ExpirationDate], [a].[ProductImagePath], COALESCE([a].[CategoryId], 0) AS [CategoryId], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[Id] IS NOT NULL THEN [a0].[NameCategory]
    ELSE N''
END AS [NameCategory]
